NICAM-DC
=========
The dynamical core component of Non-hydrostatic ICosahedral Atmospheric Model.



Contributing
-----------
This code was developped by NICAM development team
( JAMSTEC, The University of Tokyo/AORI, RIKEN/AICS ).



License
-----------
